        "page": 411,
        "ruku": 355,
        "hizbQuarter": 164,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3472,
        "text": "And a guidance and grace for those who do good,",
        "surah": {
          "number": 31,
          "name": "سُورَةُ لُقۡمَانَ",
          "englishName": "Luqman",
          "englishNameTranslation": "Luqman",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 34
        },
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 21,
        "manzil": 5,
        "page": 411,
        "ruku": 355,
        "hizbQuarter": 164,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3473,
        "text": "Who are constant in devotion, pay the zakat, and are certain of the Hereafter.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 31,
          "name": "سُورَةُ لُقۡمَانَ",
          "englishName": "Luqman",
          "englishNameTranslation": "Luqman",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 34
        },
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 21,
        "manzil": 5,
        "page": 411,
        "ruku": 355,
        "hizbQuarter": 164,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3474,
        "text": "They are on guidance from their Lord, and will prosper.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 31,
          "name": "سُورَةُ لُقۡمَانَ",
          "englishName": "Luqman",
          "englishNameTranslation": "Luqman",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 34
        },
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 21,
        "manzil": 5,
        "page": 411,
        "ruku": 355,
        "hizbQuarter": 164,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3475,
        "text": "But among men are also those who spread frivolous stories to mislead (others) from the way of God, without any knowledge, and take it lightly. For such as these the nemesis will be shameful.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 31,
          "name": "سُورَةُ لُقۡمَانَ",
          "englishName": "Luqman",
          "englishNameTranslation": "Luqman",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 34
        },
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 21,
        "manzil": 5,
        "page": 411,
        "ruku": 355,
        "hizbQuarter": 164,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3476,
        "text": "When Our verses are recited before them they turn away haughtily as though they did not hear them, as if a deafness had come into their ears. So give them tidings of a shameful punishment.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 31,
          "name": "سُورَةُ لُقۡمَانَ",
          "englishName": "Luqman",
          "englishNameTranslation": "Luqman",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 34
        },
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 21,
        "manzil": 5,
        "page": 411,
        "ruku": 355,
        "hizbQuarter": 164,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3477,
        "text": "Surely for those who believe and do the right are pleasure gardens.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 31,
          "name": "سُورَةُ لُقۡمَانَ",
          "englishName": "Luqman",
          "englishNameTranslation": "Luqman",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 34
        },
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 21,
        "manzil": 5,
        "page": 411,
        "ruku": 355,
        "hizbQuarter": 164,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3478,
        "text": "They will abide in them for ever. The promise of God is true; and He is all-mighty and all-wise.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 31,
          "name": "سُورَةُ لُقۡمَانَ",
          "englishName": "Luqman",
          "englishNameTranslation": "Luqman",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 34
        },
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 21,
        "manzil": 5,
        "page": 411,
        "ruku": 355,
        "hizbQuarter": 164,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3479,
        "text": "He created the skies without a support, as you can see, and placed stabilisers in the earth that you may dwell at ease as it revolves; and dispersed on it all varieties of creatures, and He sent down water from the skies and grew all kinds of splendid things upon it.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 31,
          "name": "سُورَةُ لُقۡمَانَ",
          "englishName": "Luqman",
          "englishNameTranslation": "Luqman",
          "revelationType": "Meccan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 34
        },
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 21,
        "manzil": 5,
        "page": 411,
        "ruku": 355,
        "hizbQuarter": 164,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3480,
        "text": "Such is God's creation. Show me now what those (they worship) beside Him have created. Surely the evil-doers are in clear error.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 31,
          "name": "سُورَةُ لُقۡمَانَ",
          "englishName": "Luqman",
          "englishNameTranslation": "Luqman",
